<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>...<span class="c5"> إِذا عدم الستْرَة هَل يُصَلِّي قَائِما:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الْمَذْهَب:</span> يُصَلِّي قَائِما.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">عِنْدهم:</span> يُصَلِّي قَاعِدا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَنْقُول:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَوْله تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَقومُوا لله قَانِتِينَ}</span> ، وَهُوَ عَام فِي جَمِيع الْأَحْوَال.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">لَهُم:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَوْله تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{فَاتَّقُوا الله مَا اسْتَطَعْتُم}</span> ، وَهُوَ لَا يَسْتَطِيع ستر عَوْرَته إِلَّا إِذا جلس فَيصَلي جَالِسا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَعْقُول:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>لِأَن الْقيام ركن من أَرْكَان الصَّلَاة وَستر الْعَوْرَة شَرط خَارج عَن الصَّلَاة،<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>